latestIgtvVideos.title: THE THREAD STORY~ @kgafest 2020
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
ART IS AN IMPORTANT PART OF OUR LIFE.IT MAKES OUR WORLD A BETTER PLACE AND BRINGS A SENSE OF ENJOYMENT AND PLEASURE.IT BRINGS BEAUTY INTO OUR WORLD.

THE KALAGHODA ARTS FESTIVAL IS INDIA'S LARGEST MULTICULTURAL AND MULTICOLOURED FESTIVAL,TAKING PLACE IN FEBRUARY EACH YEAR AT THE RAMP ART BETWEEN JEHANGIR ART GALLERY AND CHATRAPATI SHIVAJI VASTU SANGRAHALAYA(PREVIOUSLY KNOWN  AS PRINCE OF WALES MUSEUM)
IN MUMAI.

LIVING LIFE IS ABOUT MY EXPERIMENTS WITH THINGS AROUND ME,BE IT FOOD,PEOPLE,ARTS AND CRAFTS,DIYS..AND MANY MORE.IT IS ABOUT THE JOY OF MAKING SOMETHING UNIQUE,WHICH ENHANCES YOUR SPIRIT AND GIVES YOU A REASON TO LIVE LIFE POSIKTIVELY EVERY DAY,ENJOYING EVERY MOMENT OF THAT DAY,AND BIENG CREATIVE ALL THE WAY.AS CORRECTLY STATED BY AN AMERICAN POET WALT WHITMAN-" DO ANYTHING,BUT LET IT PRODUCE JOY" AND THIS IS WHAT I LIKE TO FOLLOW.

THIS 9 DAYS COLOURFUL FESTIVAL DOESNT SELL OR COLLECT TICKETS,SO PEOPLE FROM ALL WALKS OF LIFE,ACROSS SOCIAL AND ECONOMIC STRATA VISIT.I FOUND A LOT OF CULTURAL EXPOSURE OUT THERE.
EVERY BIT OF ART FROM START TO END I COULD FIND A LOT OF SIMPLE COLOURED THREAD WORK INTO A HUGE ART,CALL IT A JELLY FISH FORM TO THE MOST FAVOURITE OF ALL THE BABY GIRL IN THE WOMB,LEAVING A STONG MESSAGE TO SAVE GIRL CHILD.

AS A FASHION AND LIFESTYLE INFLUENCER AND CONTENT CREATOR I GOT A LOT OF PICTURES WHICH I UPLOADED.

THIS WAS MY  FIRST AND A BEAUTIFUL EXPERIENCE TO KGAF 2020

Wearing / @zara 
Shot/ @aesthetic.imperfectly
